 November London Eventim Apollo</strong></p><p> Despite universal acclaim from fans and critics, Cameron <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/james-cameron-calls-the-terminator-cringeworthy-in-parts-40-years-on-from-release-3795787">called the film “cringeworthy” in “parts” last year while celebrating the film&#39;s 40th Anniversary</a> .</p><p> The post<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-terminator-live-tour-coming-to-the-uk-this-year-3846938">&#39;The Terminator Live&#39; tour coming to the UK this year</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
