on">Bruce Dickinson</a> touched on interactions with their army of fans recently, relating it back to wanting to “bow out with dignity” rather than succumb to backing tracks and becoming “ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maidens-bruce-dickinson-said-hed-rather-quit-playing-live-than-become-disneyland-maiden-with-backing-tracks-3846689">Disneyland Maiden</a> “. </p><figure id="attachment_3795069" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3795069" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3795069" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/iron-maiden@2000x1270.jpg" alt="铁娘" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/iron-maiden@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/iron-maiden@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/iron-maiden@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/iron-maiden@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/iron-maiden@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/iron-maiden@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3795069" class="wp-caption-text"> Iron Maiden&#39;s Bruce Dickinson performs live. Credit: Don Arnold/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p> “Only recently this guy, a big fan, said to me, &#39;It&#39;s so great to see Maiden still doing it,&#39;” he explained. “我说，&#39;是的，我们是为了真实的！”没有失调。这个家伙说：“许多乐队现在都使用后背曲目……”我说：&#39;不！ No, no!&#39;</p><p>他补充说：“ [如果我们使用备用轨道，那就是我辞职的那一天。” “或者我们停下来的那一天。如果不是真实的，那不是少女。”</p><p> Meanwhile in the cruise discussion, Cooper commented on the Rock Hall&#39;s pivot to include non-rock acts. “It&#39;s really hard for me to put somebody, let&#39;s say, like Missy Elliott in with The Who,” he admitted (as transcribed by <a href="https://blabbermouth.net/news/alice-cooper-says-iron-maiden-should-be-inducted-into-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-they-have-their-own-army-out-there"><em>Blabbermouth</em></a> ).</p><p> Cooper added: “I was in there going, &#39;Come on. It&#39;s rock and roll bands – that&#39;s what rock is.但是后来我放松了这个想法。 Even <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dolly-parton">Dolly Parton</a> said, &#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dolly-parton-discusses-rock-hall-fame-induction-class-2022-3218870">I don&#39;t belong in the Rock And Roll Hall Of Fame</a> ,&#39; (…) but then she made a <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/dolly-parton-rockstar-review-lyrics-tracklist-3539943">rock record</a> . I don&#39;t think anybody begrudges her that, but I would still I would prefer to see an Iron Maiden in there before I would see some of these other ones.” </p><figure id="attachment_3589941" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3589941" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3589941" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/alice-cooper-uk-tour-2024.jpg" alt="Alice Cooper" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/alice-cooper-uk-tour-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/alice-cooper-uk-tour-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/alice-cooper-uk-tour-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/alice-cooper-uk-tour-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/alice-cooper-uk-tour-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/alice-cooper-uk-tour-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3589941" class="wp-caption-text"> Alice Cooper performs on stage at Alice Cooper&#39;s 21st Annual Christmas Pudding at Celebrity Theatre on December 09, 2023 in Phoenix, Arizona (CREDIT: Daniel Knighton/Getty Images)</figcaption></figure><p> Elsewhere, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-will-be-doing-stuff-weve-never-ever-done-before-on-2025-tour-teases-bruce-dickinson-3825722">Dickinson has also said the band will be “doing stuff we&#39;ve never, ever done before”</a> on the upcoming tour: “So for those of you who have bought tickets, which is like all of you, it&#39;s gonna be really, really cool. I&#39;m really looking forward to it.”</p><p>在其他处女新闻中，本月早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-announce-unrestricted-new-documentary-film-including-final-paul-dianno-interview-3846407">他们宣布了一部新的纪录片，</a>以纪念50周年纪念日，其中包括与他们的前主持人保罗·迪安诺（Paul Di&#39;anno）的最后采访， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-iron-maiden-singer-paul-dianno-dies-age-66-what-he-left-behind-will-live-on-forever-3804890">后者去年去年66岁</a>。</p><p>尽管预计将在秋季到达，但尚未共享正式的头衔和发布日期。马尔科姆·维尔维尔（Malcolm Venville）（<i>战争中的丘吉尔</i>）被任命为导演，生产来自多米尼克·弗里曼（Dominic Freeman）（<i>森林中的烈酒 - 一部</i><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/depeche-mode"><i>Depeche Mode</i></a><i>电影</i>）。</p><p>他们还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-to-release-epic-new-visual-book-chronicling-50-year-career-infinite-dreams-3845157">在秋天释放一本名为<i>“无限梦”</i>的新视觉书</a>。它将包含标志性专辑和单一艺术品的图像，乐队的过去和现在乐器，舞台道具，手写歌词和档案手工艺品。还将拍摄乐队的照片，包括一些以前看不见的照片。</p><p> Cooper meanwhile has <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alice-cooper-announces-summer-2025-uk-shows-buy-tickets-3832586">confirmed two upcoming shows for the UK later this summer, marking his only performances in Scotland and Wales for 2025</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alice-cooper-wants-iron-maiden-to-be-inducted-into-rock-roll-hall-of-fame-they-have-their-own-army-out-there-3846918">Alice Cooper wants Iron Maiden to be inducted into Rock &amp; Roll Hall Of Fame: “They have their own army out there”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
